          <element type="List" name="Personality Trait" requiredLevel="1" number="1" checksum="83aec724" isList="true" registered="6">Despite my noble birth, I do not place myself above other folk. We all have the same blood.</element>
          <element type="List" name="Personality Trait" requiredLevel="1" number="2" checksum="1aa7969e" isList="true" registered="2">The common folk love me for my kindness and generosity.</element>
          <element type="List" name="Ideal" requiredLevel="1" checksum="7daae5a2" isList="true" registered="6">Noble Obligation. It is my duty to protect and care for the people beneath me. (Good)</element>
          <element type="List" name="Bond" requiredLevel="1" checksum="6e9e8a3f" isList="true" registered="3">Nothing is more important than the other members of my family.</element>
          <element type="List" name="Flaw" requiredLevel="1" checksum="d1ee827f" isList="true" registered="5">In fact, the world does revolve around me.</element>
